  "text": "To support qualitative and quantitative monitoring of SSTL properties, a Java library has been developed. This library, named jSSTL 9 , consists of three main packages: core, util and io. Package core provides the classes used to represent SSTL formulas. These classes mimic the abstract syntax tree of formulas. This package also includes the implementations of the monitoring algorithms presented in this section and of those previously introduced in [CITATION_1] .",
